Rating: 1
Who wouldn't like beets, avocado and fennel? Unfortunately, together they just didn't work. The avocado was completely lost in the the dominant flavors of the fennel and beets. And the 4 to 1 ratio of oil to acid in the dressing was much too heavy. The whole thing never came together.

