Rating: 4
Make this recipe when beets are in season and use a variety of colors....yellow, red, orange. Not only is this a delicious salad, it makes a beautiful presentation.I have made this for my friends who swear they dont like beets and they loved it.

Rating: 3
This was really good, the avocado was a nice contrast to the crunchiness of the beets and the fennel was very refreshing. I want to make it again and again.